<tr>
<td>1</td>
<td><code>url</code></td>
<td style="text-align:center"><bubble type="string" colors="true"></bubble></td>
<td>A URL expression (see below for complete specification).<br> e.g. <code>&quot;http://google.com&quot;</code> or <code>&quot;/login&quot;</code></td>
</tr>
